{"tid":1443044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全世界入黎】手足唔好去北角！","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:28:10.000Z","uid":301460,"like":28,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa038a8340f03e643cfaec1ea0d8f04a6a46353","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我住先<br />\n我想同大家分析下點解去北角係唔好既選擇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一</span></span><br />\n班福建佬已經上曬裝備準備打義士，打起上黎我地未必有優勢。<br />\n而且，班福建佬好多係大陸落黎，佢地冇可能長時間逗留係到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二</span></span><br />\n贏同輸對我地都唔好！打輸手足傷亡慘重，就算贏，警賊黎到趁你地戰後疲態盡現，都更容易捉到你地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第三</span></span><br />\n呢次開戰不利我地形象。之前係白衫打我地，義士還手係合情合理，但今次我地既箭頭已經指向佢地。有傷亡之後老弱婦孺更加唔敢出黎做和理非抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繞過北角啊！！！唔好比班福建仆街得呈</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60129e5be6c48602d9ec27bf6e8cd365b9b559cb","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:17:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c5d1f33ffb6d0ef74e8084eddd1d4f1ce5cb96","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:18:01.000Z","msg"