nail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eyN9gj.jpg&h=0efff777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J22LbuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ22LbuE.jpg&h=8b0e7c3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55ecda6e42968c5573ce35ac577431b824e77ace","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a6553c2618d91e70fc2b4de4a20b923295c6c1b","tid":1443044,"uid":277540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eijqbuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeijqbuE.jpg&h=2734122e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eyN9gj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eyN9gj.jpg&h=0efff777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J22LbuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ22LbuE.jpg&h=8b0e7c3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895c0bbb10decdbd91883161396dd3928e9fb9ce","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d842f6536892790b156d97beb586ad068e6d67d5","tid":1443044,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:21:18.000Z","msg":"擺明警黑合作"},{"pid":"5aa3a06cb6ec61c9d8d2710f00be362d8e7d5440","tid":1443044,"uid":160037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"依家北角一埋防暴（冇上gear)睇住啲福建人，砲台山都有。<br />\n<br />\n其實最好就係等佢兩班人罰下企，曬下太陽<br />\n<br />\n如果入北角我覺得真係唔值"},{"pid":"735938d4ddc0aca987bc66b050ebdb02de8ef905","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e884897637aef92490ea3ab3ce5d32d4177939","tid":1443044,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:23:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=d35976fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">47,412</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 14:23）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"1bc90f8c493608e6ff09b7f854661cbd92b8c35a","tid":1443044,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"差佬已經喺北角 炮台山已經佈防 形成包圍網<br />\n請各位手足獨立思考 自行判斷仲去唔去"},{"pid":"1eadeab7ff727261c13922a201b8a1e5a4566c35","tid":1443044,"uid":294930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"地理問題，向東區只可以經北角。一係搭車。"},{"pid":"846f36a8a28f37e638370be01ab221c1b8d4165a","tid":1443044,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"主動去比人夾擊太on9<br />\n千祈唔好去"},{"pid":"50b2bbbb98190f10a873a8842c22718068bf81a6","tid":1443044,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"b810df488788a200236fb71b66b26b356c9b4a1d","tid":1443044,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa3a06cb6ec61c9d8d2710f00be362d8e7d5440","tid":1443044,"uid":160037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"依家北角一埋防暴（冇上gear)睇住啲福建人，砲台山都有。<br />\n<br />\n其實最好就係等佢兩班人罰下企，曬下太陽<br />\n<br />\n如果入北角我覺得真係唔值"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"咪去北角送頭，要玩就去中西區玩中資！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1443040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1443040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc515864bb16c1e5466e5806c3b6ac739eff9e3e","tid":1443044,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a6553c2618d91e70fc2b4de4a20b923295c6c1b","tid":1443044,"uid":277540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eijqbuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeijqbuE.jpg&h=2734122e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eyN9gj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eyN9gj.jpg&h=0efff777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J22LbuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ22LbuE.jpg&h=8b0e7c3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"推俾係維園手足知"},{"pid":"c92466a05eead07fa287fae77c62ef92f862c294","tid":1443044,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"1400  北角錦屏街大量防暴警握手  黑社會 及 同鄉會  出動了"},{"pid":"5adf04c1bab0bc3463b367097732e87f9c144466","tid":1443044,"uid":115799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xueE0pA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxueE0pA.jpg&h=41dafb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14:24"},{"pid":"ff08bfdae960ee2ba943aba9d1bca600607294bd","tid":1443044,"uid":285654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa038a8340f03e643cfaec1ea0d8f04a6a46353","tid":1443044,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我住先<br />\n我想同大家分析下點解去北角係唔好既選擇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一</span></span><br />\n班福建佬已經上曬裝備準備打義士，打起上黎我地未必有優勢。<br />\n而且，班福建佬好多係大陸落黎，佢地冇可能長時間逗留係到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二</span></span><br />\n贏同輸對我地都唔好！打輸手足傷亡慘重，就算贏，警賊黎到趁你地戰後疲態盡現，都更容易捉到你地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第三</span></span><br />\n呢次開戰不利我地形象。之前係白衫打我地，義士還手係合情合理，但今次我地既箭頭已經指向佢地。有傷亡之後老弱婦孺更加唔敢出黎做和理非抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繞過北角啊！！！唔好比班福建仆街得呈</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ab6cb646990e33cda48c88a6cfab371429abaae","tid":1443044,"uid":294930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b810df488788a200236fb71b66b26b356c9b4a1d","tid":1443044,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa3a06cb6ec61c9d8d2710f00be362d8e7d5440","tid":1443044,"uid":160037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"依家北角一埋防暴（冇上gear)睇住啲福建人，砲台山都有。<br />\n<br />\n其實最好就係等佢兩班人罰下企，曬下太陽<br />\n<br />\n如果入北角我覺得真係唔值"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"咪去北角送頭，要玩就去中西區玩中資！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1443040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1443040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}